    cd_priv_perm_cam_h:"Camera & Photo Library Access",
    cd_priv_perm_cam_p:"The App uses your device's camera and photo library to <strong>attach receipt photos and images to transactions</strong>. Selected images are processed entirely on your device. No image data is transmitted to any server or third party unless you explicitly choose to back up your data via Google Drive.",
    cd_priv_perm_fin_h:"Financial Data",
    cd_priv_perm_fin_p:"All your financial data - including <strong>transactions, accounts, credit cards, loans, budgets, and categories</strong> - is stored locally on your device using an encrypted local database. This data never leaves your device unless you explicitly choose to export or back it up.",
    cd_priv_perm_notif_h:"Notifications",
    cd_priv_perm_notif_p:"The App may request notification permission to send you <strong>bill reminders, budget alerts, and recurring transaction notifications</strong>. You can disable notifications at any time through your device settings.",
    cd_priv_securityapp_h:"App Security",
    cd_priv_securityapp_p:"CashDiary offers robust security features to protect your financial data:",
    cd_priv_securityapp_li1:"<strong>6-digit PIN lock</strong> - Required to open the App, keeping your data private",
    cd_priv_securityapp_li2:"<strong>Biometric authentication</strong> - Supports fingerprint and face recognition as a convenient alternative to PIN",
    cd_priv_securityapp_li3:"<strong>Password hashing</strong> - Your PIN is hashed using <strong>PBKDF2 with 100,000 iterations</strong>, making it extremely difficult to crack even if device data is accessed",
    cd_priv_securityapp_li4:"<strong>Encrypted local database</strong> - All financial data is stored in an encrypted database on your device",
    cd_priv_securityapp_li5:"<strong>Auto-lock</strong> - The App automatically locks when you switch to another app or after a period of inactivity",
    cd_priv_gdrive_h:"Google Drive Backup",
    cd_priv_gdrive_p:"The App offers an <strong>optional</strong> Google Drive backup feature. When you choose to use this feature:",
    cd_priv_gdrive_li1:"The App requests access to Google Drive's app-specific storage (<code>appDataFolder</code>) only.",
    cd_priv_gdrive_li2:"Your financial data is encrypted in transit (HTTPS/TLS) and stored in a private folder that only this App can access.",
    cd_priv_gdrive_li3:"No other files on your Google Drive are accessed, read, or modified.",
    cd_priv_gdrive_li4:"You can disconnect your Google account or delete the backup data at any time through the App's settings.",
    cd_priv_export_h:"Local Backup & Export",
    cd_priv_export_p1:"The App provides multiple ways to export and back up your data locally:",
